-- Lafarge, CRH Among Contenders for India's Murli Industries, Standard Says
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-06-23T01:49:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/lafarge-crh-among-contenders-for-india-s-murli-industries-standard-says.html

          
          
             Lafarge SA, HeidelbergCement AG, CRH
Plc and Italcementi SpA are among four global cement companies
that have expressed interest in buying India’s Murli Industries
Ltd., the Business Standard newspaper reported, citing two
officials it didn’t identify.  
